title: Community presale on xDAI + LBP + Uniswap liquidity mining
body:
This proposal is for distributing the 85m HOPR tokens to both existing members and also to new members as follows:

- 20m HOPR community whiltelisted (whitelist is the Genesis DAO) presale on xDAI token price $0.05: The HOPR Genesis DAO currently has about 3000 members so that would make about 6600 HOPR per person. If the cap does not get reached within 24h, remove the personal cap so that the rest of the community can buy in. In this way the DAO could raise up to 1m DAI which is a good starting capital for LBP.
 
- 59m HOPR Balancer LBP on main net: This is open for anyone, does not require any KYC and starts a price finding of secondary market. The proceeds from the presale start the LBP. Starting price should be at least $0.3 and then fall from there over 72h similar to PERP (if people buy, the price might also go higher).

- 6m liquidity mining on Uniswap: Distributed over 3 months, this incentivizes liquidity providers to not just dump their tokens but actually keep liquidity on Uniswap.

None of these processes require KYC, the community presale is cheap because of xDAI and all preserves the privacy of the HOPR community and allows for a fair distribution. That should serve everyone in the community.
